headline: Camden Property Trust Announces Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Release and Conference Call Dates
summary: HOUSTON, January 13, 2025--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") announced today that its fourth quarter 2024 earnings will be released after the market closes on Thursday, February 6, 2025. Management will host a conference call on the following day, Friday, February 7, 2025, at 10:00 AM Central Time.
